@UserService.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5161
@token = <your-jwt-token-here>

### Login
POST {{UserService.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Profile (requires auth)
GET {{UserService.API_HostAddress}}/api/secure/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin Only (requires Admin role)
GET {{UserService.API_HostAddress}}/api/secure/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Management (requires Admin or Manager role)
GET {{UserService.API_HostAddress}}/api/secure/management
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Staff (requires Admin, Manager, or User role)
GET {{UserService.API_HostAddress}}/api/secure/staff
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reports (requires Admin, Manager, or Analyst role)
GET {{UserService.API_HostAddress}}/api/secure/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
